{"tid":2003482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不同意某會員叫人杯葛登記口罩","createTime":"2020-05-06T00:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T01:59:33.000Z","uid":26770,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c74902646493c457daff617949a61d39d13c73e5","tid":2003482,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:17:58.000Z","msg":"唔登記可以係係海外/本身搵到錢用一次性口罩/有大把口罩懶填表<br />\n唔一定導向係不信任林鄭臭西的結論<br />\n<br />\n我鼓勵大家填表<br />\nha 系統一早安左後門比香港警魔<br />\n我睇唔到登記口罩會增加香港納粹警魔的情報<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家登記口罩係會影響派件時間, 藍絲又會屌</span>"},{"pid":"fb61bfbd98203b61516d506573fd02b3bd4a526a","tid":2003482,"uid":280648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:50:42.000Z","msg":"其實都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府有齊曬我哋啲資料"},{"pid":"9f97be56abfd0f98fdb420a8b796321de3295870","tid":2003482,"uid":213877,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:58:08.000Z","msg":"你要口罩就登記，唔買就咪柒登記<br />\n<br />\n就咁撚簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9249595f34c66a6a38ecc4204ad7eecf3987a7ba","tid":2003482,"uid":267801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T00:58:52.000Z","msg":"遊行示威時可以用同一種口罩。"},{"pid":"7723cb081cd1aef9a2c060279c5f93727ae22c55","tid":2003482,"uid":3860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"支持政府既實登記<br />\n<br />\n驚黑警拎資料既不如擔心唔登記=送資料好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識玩既一定係用唔用都登記，等佢地出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d534b633aed54ac2f7e15714530e8739853b45","tid":2003482,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T01:02:49.000Z","msg":"已經有班垃圾殭屍毛用應唔應該登記口罩去分化<br />\n分兩派扮對屌分化<br />\n<br />\n林鄭邊會做好事, 咩都有政治目的"},{"pid":"4a27ef2a52d00129ee5ba069ae66b94d0d85ad80","tid"